    <div class="container-wide pt-16 pb-14">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
        <span class="eyebrow">Measurement</span>
        <span class="font-mono text-xs text-ink-400">7 June 2026</span>
        <span class="font-mono text-xs text-ink-400">11 min read</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="mt-5 max-w-3xl font-display text-4xl font-bold leading-tight grad-text md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
        How to Measure GEO
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-ink-200">
        <strong class="text-white">Measuring GEO means tracking how often, how accurately, and with what sentiment AI engines cite your brand — not just whether clicks arrive.</strong> This guide covers the four core GEO metrics, how to capture each one, the tooling available at every budget, and a six-step measurement framework you can implement immediately. It applies equally to measuring AI optimization (the US-spelled variant of the same discipline) across ChatGPT, Perplexity, Gemini, Copilot, and Google AI Overviews.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

