              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-white">Pull AI referral traffic</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-ink-300">Session volume, engagement rate, and conversions from GA4 AI Referral channel group</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="transition hover:bg-white/[.02]">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs text-[var(--accent)]">5</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-white">Score sentiment and accuracy</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-ink-300">Description accuracy flags, sentiment distribution, entity correction priorities</td>
